items.bio: I'm Obnoxious | Feelings fly away like a leaf,moving & stopping,no one cares.
If I'm not here for work, then I should at least be having fun!

I'm no perfect girl but who is?
I just live and love like it's the end of the world.
I am too busy getting stronger.

My life is like a big party; I just dance all my worries away because I know that God is my DJ.

Twitter: @NapoleonWjangco
IG/LINE: NapoleonWijangco
My goal is to really just check in to every damn place i step into. Let's make Foursquare a life game!
"Teach us to number our days, so that we may apply our hearts unto wisdom." - The Bible, Psalms, 90:12
